{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face off against Satan's demonic goat army. As hellish goat hordes emerge from cursed portals, your mission is to kill Satan's goat army as they come out of gateways and take down the Devil himself in a final showdown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Goat Massacre is a fast-paced first-person shooter taking place in a meadowed farmland. As hellish portals bring Satan's goat army to Earth, you must fight hoards of goats in increasingly difficulty, closing portals and fighting Satan himself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set in a realistic world, arm yourself with assault rifles, shotguns, and grenades as you take on the progressing difficulty of the goatpocalypse. Fight through demonic hordes and blast those horned beasts back to the underworld to reclaim your life and restore order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even after defeating Satan, you can challenge him as many times as you'd like, but each time becomes more and more challenging, making for virtually infinite gameplay.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730500565","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259390/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1730500565","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259390/cf704faa0edd914ed4c3d78d685ed784a3249089/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730500565","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259390/cf704faa0edd914ed4c3d78d685ed784a3249089/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730500565","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face off against Satan's demonic goat army. As hellish goat hordes emerge from cursed portals, your mission is to kill Satan's g